OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,FOrganisers of 'Manchester Village
OL,7,FPride' have announced the theme for
OL,8,Fthe parade at the city's renewed Pride
OL,9,Fevent.
OL,11,FAdopting a key line from The Wizard of
OL,12,FOz, the 'No Place Like Home' theme
OL,13,Foffers the opportunity for community
OL,14,Fgroups to celebrate a homecoming and
OL,15,Fsafe landing for Pride in the city
OL,16,Fafter recent uncertainties, as well as
OL,17,Fa chance to honour the city of
OL,18,FManchester itself as a welcoming place
OL,19,Ffor all.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
