PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774012288
OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,FIt comes after the collapse of the
OL,7,Fprevious Manchester Pride
OL,8,Forganisation, where there was a risk
OL,9,Fthat core Pride traditions ` including
OL,10,Fthe Parade, the Village Party and the
OL,11,FVigil ` could be lost.
OL,13,FIn response, the Village
OL,14,Fcommunitystepped forward to protect
OL,15,FPride's future, now looked after by a
OL,16,Fgroup of volunteers.
OL,18,FManchester Village Pride received
OL,19,F#120,000 in loans from Village venues,
OL,20,Freflecting the goals of local LGBTQ+
OL,21,Fbusinesses working to safeguard Pride.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774012288
OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,FThe parade will take place on Saturday
OL,7,F29 August and will work its way
OL,8,Fthrough the city via a route ` still
OL,9,Fto be determined ` that will conclude
OL,10,Fin the Village; the place where Pride
OL,11,Fbegan in Manchester four decades ago.
OL,13,FAnnouncing the theme, Carl Austin-
OL,14,FBehan, one of the founding board
OL,15,Fmembers and spokesperson for
OL,16,FManchester Village Pride CIC, said:
OL,17,F"The parade is one of the most
OL,18,Fimportant and iconic events during
OL,19,FPride Weekend in Manchester.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774012288
OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,F"It's a time for the community to come
OL,7,Ftogether with people from all walks of
OL,8,Flife to celebrate, listen, and show
OL,9,Fvisibility for LGBTQ+ life in
OL,10,FManchester and beyond.
OL,12,F"'No Place Like Home' is a very apt
OL,13,Ftheme for this year, allowing us to
OL,14,Fpay tribute to Pride's roots in the
OL,15,FVillage; the home of our amazing
OL,16,Fcommunity and everything that
OL,17,FManchester Village Pride stands for `
OL,18,Ffrom our LGBTQ+ businesses and
OL,19,Fcharities to performers and patrons.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774012288
OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,F"I can't wait to see how the community
OL,7,Fresponds and interprets the theme, as
OL,8,FI think there is so much to go on!
OL,10,F"The parade is one of the cornerstone
OL,11,Felements of the weekend, alongside the
OL,12,Fpoignant Candlelit Vigil, that we want
OL,13,Fas many people as possible to attend.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
