PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774012288
OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,F"Both elements are, and always will
OL,7,Fbe, free to attend; however, we do ask
OL,8,Fthat those who would like to enjoy the
OL,9,Fwider celebrations ` including the
OL,10,Fparty and performances in the Village
OL,11,F` purchase a weekend wristband or
OL,12,Findividual day pass to ensure that
OL,13,Ffunding goes towards safe event
OL,14,Fdelivery, as well as supporting LGBTQ+
OL,15,Fcharities, grassroots organisations,
OL,16,Fand vital community services.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
