PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774012288
OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,F"With it being our first Manchester
OL,7,FVillage Pride event under transparent
OL,8,Fmanagement, we also need to be clear
OL,9,Fwith people that we need them to make
OL,10,Ftheir commitment as early as possible
OL,11,Fby purchasing their wristband or day
OL,12,Fpasses.
OL,14,F"This will ensure that we can lock in
OL,15,FLGBTQ+ talent and make sure event
OL,16,Fplanning is smoothly and fairly
OL,17,Ffinanced ` the success of Manchester
OL,18,FVillage Pride is in the community's
OL,19,Fhands, and now is the time to show up!"
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
