OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,FThis year's parade is supported by
OL,7,FManchester City Council.
OL,9,FCllr Bev Craig, Leader of Manchester
OL,10,FCity Council, said: "Pride is such an
OL,11,Fimportant event for our city, and
OL,12,Fafter concerns over its future, it's
OL,13,Fgreat that it's firmly back on the
OL,14,Fcalendar.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
