FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774012288
OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,F"The phrase 'No Place Like Home' has
OL,7,Fadded resonance this year after the
OL,8,Fevent was saved for the city by
OL,9,FManchester Village Pride CIC and its
OL,10,Fsupporters, including the Council. We
OL,11,Fare proud to have played our part,
OL,12,Fincluding funding the popular parade
OL,13,Felement that people know and love.
OL,15,F"Pride is more than just an annual
OL,16,Fboost for our city's hospitality
OL,17,Fsector, as significant as this. It's a
OL,18,Fcelebration of Manchester's LGBTQ+
OL,19,Fcommunity; an event which has been
OL,20,Fpart of the fabric of the city for
OL,21,Fmore than 40 years."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
