PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774012288
OL,3,CPride parade returns to Manchester
OL,4,Cwith 'No Place like Home' theme
OL,6,FAlong with the announcement of the
OL,7,Ftheme, Manchester Village Pride CIC
OL,8,Fhas opened applications for those who
OL,9,Fare interested in taking part in the
OL,10,Fparade on the day.
OL,12,FIn support of the local community,
OL,13,Ffree entry will be offered to all
OL,14,FLGBTQ+ charities and grassroots
OL,15,Fgroups, whilst commercial entries will
OL,16,Fbe required to pay an entry fee to
OL,17,Fhelp subsidise the costs for community
OL,18,Fentries.
OL,20,FListen to the ITV News' entertainment
OL,21,Fpodcast, Unscripted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
